---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Tools | Manopause"
  description="Practical tools for de-escalation, boundary-setting, documentation, and digital safety in difficult relationships."
>
  <main class="tools-page">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Tools</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
          Practical strategies you can use today. From de-escalating conflict to 
          setting boundaries to staying safe ‚Äî these tools help you take action.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container content-wrapper">
      
      <!-- Introduction -->
      <section class="intro">
        <p>
          Knowledge is important, but sometimes you need something you can actually do. 
          These practical tools give you concrete strategies for common challenging situations.
        </p>
        <p>
          Each tool includes scripts you can adapt, step-by-step guidance, and important 
          safety considerations.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Tool Cards -->
      <section class="tool-grid">
        
        <a href="/tools/de-escalation" class="tool-card de-escalation">
          <div class="tool-icon">üå°Ô∏è</div>
          <div class="tool-content">
            <h2>De-escalation</h2>
            <p class="read-time">12 min read</p>
            <p class="description">
              Learn how to lower the temperature when conflict is heating up. 
              Techniques for calming yourself and the situation before things escalate.
            </p>
            <ul class="includes">
              <li>Escalation ladder</li>
              <li>Breathing techniques</li>
              <li>Structured break protocol</li>
              <li>Repair attempts</li>
            </ul>
            <span class="learn-more">Explore tool ‚Üí</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/boundaries" class="tool-card boundaries">
          <div class="tool-icon">üõ°Ô∏è</div>
          <div class="tool-content">
            <h2>Boundaries</h2>
            <p class="read-time">15 min read</p>
            <p class="description">
              How to set limits that protect you without escalating conflict. 
              The difference between boundaries and ultimatums, and what to do 
              when boundaries are tested.
            </p>
            <ul class="includes">
              <li>Boundary formula</li>
              <li>Script examples</li>
              <li>Testing patterns</li>
              <li>The broken record technique</li>
            </ul>
            <span class="learn-more">Explore tool ‚Üí</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/documentation" class="tool-card documentation">
          <div class="tool-icon">üìù</div>
          <div class="tool-content">
            <h2>Documentation</h2>
            <p class="read-time">10 min read</p>
            <p class="description">
              How to keep records of what's happening without obsessing over it. 
              Documentation that grounds you in reality and protects you if needed.
            </p>
            <ul class="includes">
              <li>Incident log format</li>
              <li>Facts vs. interpretations</li>
              <li>Secure storage options</li>
              <li>Timeline template</li>
            </ul>
            <span class="learn-more">Explore tool ‚Üí</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/digital-safety" class="tool-card digital-safety">
          <div class="tool-icon">üîê</div>
          <div class="tool-content">
            <h2>Digital Safety</h2>
            <p class="read-time">14 min read</p>
            <p class="description">
              Technology can be used to monitor, control, and harass. Learn how to 
              assess your devices, communicate safely, and protect your privacy.
            </p>
            <ul class="includes">
              <li>Device safety checks</li>
              <li>Safe communication methods</li>
              <li>Smart home awareness</li>
              <li>Leaving safely</li>
            </ul>
            <span class="learn-more">Explore tool ‚Üí</span>
          </div>
        </a>

      </section>

      <!-- Quick Access Section -->
      <section class="quick-access">
        <h2>Quick Access</h2>
        <p>Need something specific right now?</p>
        
        <div class="quick-grid">
          <div class="quick-card">
            <h3>üìû In a heated moment?</h3>
            <p>Try the <a href="/tools/de-escalation#quick-reference">De-escalation Quick Reference</a></p>
          </div>

          <div class="quick-card">
            <h3>‚úçÔ∏è Need a script?</h3>
            <p>See <a href="/tools/boundaries#common-scripts">Common Boundary Scripts</a></p>
          </div>

          <div class="quick-card">
            <h3>üì± Worried about device safety?</h3>
            <p>Check the <a href="/tools/digital-safety#device-check">Device Safety Checklist</a></p>
          </div>

          <div class="quick-card">
            <h3>üìã Need to log an incident?</h3>
            <p>Use the <a href="/tools/documentation#incident-format">Incident Log Format</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Using These Tools -->
      <section class="usage-tips">
        <h2>How to Use These Tools</h2>
        
        <div class="tip-grid">
          <div class="tip">
            <div class="tip-number">1</div>
            <div class="tip-content">
              <h3>Start Where You Are</h3>
              <p>
                You don't need to read everything. Pick the tool that addresses 
                your most pressing concern right now.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="tip">
            <div class="tip-number">2</div>
            <div class="tip-content">
              <h3>Practice When Calm</h3>
              <p>
                Try techniques like breathing or boundary scripts when you're not 
                in crisis. It makes them easier to use when you need them.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="tip">
            <div class="tip-number">3</div>
            <div class="tip-content">
              <h3>Adapt to Your Situation</h3>
              <p>
                Every relationship is different. Adjust the scripts and strategies 
                to fit your specific circumstances.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="tip">
            <div class="tip-number">4</div>
            <div class="tip-content">
              <h3>Safety First</h3>
              <p>
                These tools are designed with safety in mind, but you know your 
                situation best. If something feels risky, trust your instincts.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Safety Warning -->
      <section class="safety-warning">
        <h2>‚ö†Ô∏è Important Safety Note</h2>
        <p>
          These tools are most effective in relationships with high conflict but not 
          severe danger. If you are in an abusive relationship, some of these strategies 
          (especially boundary-setting and documentation) could escalate risk.
        </p>
        <p>
          Before taking action in a dangerous situation, please consult with a domestic 
          violence advocate. Call the <a href="tel:18007997233">National DV Hotline: 1-800-799-7233</a> 
          for safety planning support.
        </p>
        <a href="/get-help" class="btn btn-safety">Get Help Resources ‚Üí</a>
      </section>

      <!-- Related Content -->
      <section class="related">
        <h2>Related Learning</h2>
        <div class="related-grid">
          <a href="/learn/what-is-abuse" class="related-card">
            <span class="related-icon">üìö</span>
            <span class="related-text">What Is Abuse?</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/learn/trauma-responses" class="related-card">
            <span class="related-icon">üß†</span>
            <span class="related-text">Trauma & Stress</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/learn/patterns" class="related-card">
            <span class="related-icon">üîÑ</span>
            <span class="related-text">Patterns Library</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/start-here" class="related-card">
            <span class="related-icon">üß≠</span>
            <span class="related-text">Assessment</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .tools-page {
    --primary: #2563eb;
    --secondary: #7c3aed;
    --success: #059669;
    --warning: #d97706;
    --danger: #dc2626;
  }

  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--secondary) 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    opacity: 0.95;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .content-wrapper {
    padding: 3rem 1rem;
  }

  .intro {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .intro p {
    color: #475569;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  /* Tool Grid */
  .tool-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(380px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .tool-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .tool-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .tool-card.de-escalation:hover { border-color: #f97316; }
  .tool-card.boundaries:hover { border-color: var(--primary); }
  .tool-card.documentation:hover { border-color: var(--secondary); }
  .tool-card.digital-safety:hover { border-color: var(--success); }

  .tool-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .tool-content h2 {
    color: #1e293b;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .read-time {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .description {
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .includes {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .includes li {
    background: #f1f5f9;
    color: #475569;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  .learn-more {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  /* Quick Access */
  .quick-access {
    background: #f8fafc;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .quick-access h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #1e293b;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .quick-access > p {
    color: #64748b;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .quick-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .quick-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
  }

  .quick-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #1e293b;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .quick-card p {
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .quick-card a {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Usage Tips */
  .usage-tips {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .usage-tips h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #1e293b;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .tip-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .tip {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .tip-number {
    width: 2.5rem;
    height: 2.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--secondary) 100%);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .tip-content h3 {
    color: #1e293b;
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .tip-content p {
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* Safety Warning */
  .safety-warning {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef2f2 0%, #fee2e2 100%);
    border: 1px solid #fecaca;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .safety-warning h2 {
    color: #991b1b;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .safety-warning p {
    color: #b91c1c;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .safety-warning a:not(.btn) {
    color: #991b1b;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .btn-safety {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #dc2626;
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-safety:hover {
    background: #b91c1c;
  }

  /* Related */
  .related h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #1e293b;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .related-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .related-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
    background: #f8fafc;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #475569;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }

  .related-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .related-icon {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .related-text {
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .tool-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .tool-card {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .quick-access {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .safety-warning {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
